Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Layer:10 LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的事實 就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音…玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何我會變成真神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所認定的神絕對不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白肉體是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:04:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死的意思 只是把肉體放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說千砂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（這種地方 我不存在也沒所謂）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說也對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓網絡協議進化的更趨完整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 你的確做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但協議也只是協議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我已在更高層次之處加上我才知道的密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面有什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把情報放在那資料裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎樣的情報呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括我和那英利政美的思想 履歷 記錄 情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣做到底有何意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以匿名的方式存在於網絡上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便能永遠生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能控制網上的數據 支配一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種存在方式 應該稱呼為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實神是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是能以普通的方式存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在上位的話 也不能稱為神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 它是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 是被做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經不再需要肉體了 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 把書收進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何突然變成如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底做錯過什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直不敢胡說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都很小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但果然還是變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我真的不該擁有肉體？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這現實世界已不再需要有你存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟你道別了 玲音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的工作已完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在短短的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒好好對待妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從此你自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 其實從開始你就自由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不能跟你說再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我真的喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒有一般家庭的融洽生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但曾是玲音父親的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也感到非常光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要留下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實你不只是一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你到網絡上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會有人來歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該是這樣子的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要做什麼？玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你的世界 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是否做了個假的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據東方傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士團的起源似乎是圓桌騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在還沒有互聯網時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們利用人與人之間所構成的網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來收集所需要的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要做什麼？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS…KNIGHTS到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的想知道嗎？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為作為計算機網絡上的神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定要擁有崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到別的地方好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得這很無聊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 要不要來我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昌幸你不來也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太郎不會跟你這種小鬼玩的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼話 你也是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩年輕是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太郎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡新聞說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在說名單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼名單？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KNIGHTS成員的名單
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在網絡上流傳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我替他注射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽我在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個換媽媽你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快來的話我就繼續玩了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽你好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要繼續玩了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天世界各地出現連串自殺事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各地警方正全力追查原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自殺身亡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據消息報導
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是網絡上一個名叫KNIGHTS的組織之中的成員…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們為何要這樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是我們客戶的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把全世界的KNIGHTS成員找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就負責一切善後工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網上世界並非特別的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充其量只是真實世界的某部份備案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實你在網上已全無存在目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正已平安無事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總覺得你像是有守護神在保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天那英利政美殘留的計算機程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要它從網絡上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們那位顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要我們將那程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠消失在網絡上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們…不需要神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 無論現實或網上都是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們無法了解你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我們很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可說是很不可思議的…感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些崇拜的人已不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼照你所說的 神已經不存在了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不是所有人都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要還有一個崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:19:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就還是能當神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真討厭啊 就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還能以你所存在 都是我的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原本就是網絡的創造者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是網上的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網絡童話的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現實世界的岩倉玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一個程序
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類所做出來的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本沒有一個實體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
